snippet.title: Stay Safe: Labyrinth of the Mad (PC, Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
A roguelike adventure for PC where you try to escape a deep dungeon of 35 floors. Along the way you'll encounter champions, copies of other real players! By defeating them, you will become the new champions for others to defeat.... stay safe, okay?

Now available on Steam: http://bit.ly/StaySafeSteam

More info: http://staysafe.yellowcakegames.com/
Discord: http://bit.ly/YellowcakeDiscord
